data.description: ALL TVS, TV MOUNTS, WINE RACKS & WINE INCLUDED! Built in 2021, this John Houston home in Mansfield's South Pointe community impresses on all levels. Upon entrance, you will be greeted by oversized windows that flood the home with natural light. The 20 foot ceilings enhance the spaciousness of the home through the main floor. Off the entrance, the second living room features a breathtaking wine wall. The kitchen is a dream with oversized island, gas range double ovens, gas range, pot filler & large pantry. The kitchen opens to the primary living room with a jaw dropping gas fireplace and view of the covered patio and backyard. When time to unwind, you'll find the luxurious primary suite on the main level. The ensuite feature herringbone tile floors, dual sinks, separate shower and oversized tub along with oversized walk in closet. Travel upstairs and enjoy the the contemporary horizontal stair railing as you discover the sizeable game room, two bedrooms and full bath.
